048-03-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe home features two bedrooms, a combined living room and kitchen, and a laboratory-library, interspersed with shaded outdoor terraces from which to observe local wildlife, like jaguars and howler monkeys.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1500\" height=\"2008\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/circular-off-grid-home-architecture-121124-1048-04.jpg\" alt=\"A modern circular off-grid home that\u0026#39;s raised up on stilts.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/circular-off-grid-home-architecture-121124-1048-04.jpg 1500w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/circular-off-grid-home-architecture-121124-1048-04-940x1258.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/circular-off-grid-home-architecture-121124-1048-04-800x1071.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/circular-off-grid-home-architecture-121124-1048-04-768x1028.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/circular-off-grid-home-architecture-121124-1048-04-1147x1536.jpg 1147w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe expansive roof protects the house from the region’s intense rain and sun, while the hyperbolic form directs rainwater towards the sides, where it cascades into natural streams. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1500\" height=\"2008\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/circular-off-grid-home-architecture-121124-1048-05.jpg\" alt=\"A modern circular off-grid home that\u0026#39;s raised up on stilts.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/circular-off-grid-home-architecture-121124-1048-05.jpg 1500w, https://www.conte